# 🤖 AWS EC2 Discord Controller — Multi-Instance + Multi-Region Edition

Control **multiple AWS EC2 instances across multiple regions** from a single Discord bot using slash commands, with automatic start/stop scheduling via EventBridge Scheduler. One Lambda, one bot, unlimited instances, any region — each addressable by a friendly name.

```
/start-ec2  name:gameserver     ← ap-south-1
/stop-ec2   name:devbox         ← us-east-1
/status-ec2 name:all            ← entire fleet, every region
```

