## Commands Reference

| Command | Example | What happens |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `/start-ec2` | `name:gameserver` | Starts that instance (in its own region) |
| `/stop-ec2` | `name:all` | Stops **every** mapped instance across **all** regions |
| `/reboot-ec2` | `name:gitlab` | Reboots that instance |
| `/status-ec2` | `name:all` | Fleet summary — one compact line each, region shown |
| `/status-ec2` | `name:devbox` | Full detailed report for one instance |

